message.content:
1. Fifty-four bone marrows were performed.
2. There were 27 standard bone marrows.
3. There were 27 OBM bone marrows.
4. The bone marrows were performed by 11 fellows.
5. The bone marrows were performed under observation.
6. The bone marrows were performed under supervision.
7. The observation and supervision were done by 3 attending hematologists.
8. The observation and supervision were also done by 1 research technologist.

messages.content:
Statement: Fifty-four bone marrows (27 standard and 27 OBM) were performed by 11 fellows under the observation and supervision of 3 attending hematologists and 1 research technologist.

List all the facts we explicitly know from the statement. Make each fact as atomic as possible.
